title: MT1 Practice Exam Autograder
question:
At this point the autograders are updated for:
2020w1-mt1
2020w1-mt2

2020w2-mt1
2020w2-mt2

2021w1-f

2021w1-mt1

In other words, in the list of exams at https://cs110.students.cs.ubc.ca/exams/ all the exams with lowercase names have autograders. You should be able to submit and get feedback on your practice work. 
Remember that:
 Practice exams are for your practice only. They are indicative of questions we have asked before, do not assume they include every kind of question we might ever ask.  Also practice with problem sets, labs, and the problem bank.
The autograders for the practice exams are intended to be illustrative.  Do not assume that the exact details of what one autograder checks will be what happens on the midterm.
